The staff are friendly, whether you are talking to the parking valet or the Front desk personnel.	When we got there the parking was very tight to get in off the street and into the underground where the valet was.	Parking valet and reception staff were friendly and quick to provide good service.	The only two negatives I would say were the price for parking and the slow internet speed.	Everyone on the staff from the valet parking to the front desk staff to the bellman went out of their way to be helpful.	The room we got was on the top floor but facing the alley and parking garage.